{
  "note": "Canonical Streamable-HTTP MCP client session for the Mind Ontology hosted connector. Replayed in-process by agentctx-hosted-connector-smoke-fixtures.test.mjs against the inline snapshot below — no network, no deploy, no credential. This is a golden conversation fixture, not a live transcript.",
  "snapshot": {
